## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| `StepperItemContext` default | `null` | Distinguishes "inside item" vs "standalone" usage in `StepperContent` |
| `StepperContent` step resolution | `itemCtx?.step ?? stepProp` | Works inside items (no prop needed) AND standalone (explicit `step` prop) |
| No Radix primitive | Pure React | No Radix stepper primitive exists |
| Separator position | Inside `StepperItem` (last child) | Reads `isCompleted` from item context; placed after `StepperTrigger` in horizontal items, between trigger and content in vertical |
| Separator visibility outside item | Supported via `className` prop | User places separator between items and sets margin manually |
| `"use client"` | Yes, on both component files | `useState` + click handlers require client runtime |

